stem:[= \"lg\" {1}/{p(x,y)} \" Hart\"]

stem:[= \"ln\" {1}/{p(x,y)} \"unitsml(nat)\"]

is the joint probability of events stem:[x] and stem:[y]
"""@en ;
  skos:note """See <<iec60050-171,droploc%locality:item=\"171-07-20\">>."""@en ;
